cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with medical image analysis using deep learning techniques, specifically for the task of diagnosing IPMN from multisequence MRI. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of pre-trained models and transfer learning also suggests the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The handling of volumetric data and fusion of multiple modalities suggests the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of deep learning for medical diagnosis suggests the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
